a result of the modified retrospective adoption of Accounting Standards Update (ASU) No. 2016-02, Leases (Topic 842), as amended. Effective January
1, 2018, the Company changed its method for recognizing revenue as a result of the modified retrospective adoption of ASU No. 2014-09, Revenue from
