Our cash equivalents (money market securities), short-term investments (certificate and time deposits) and nonrefundable customer deposits are
recorded at amortized cost, and the respective carrying amounts approximate fair values. Short-term investments and nonrefundable customer deposits
are recorded in “Other current assets” and our investment securities are recorded in “Other Assets” on the consolidated balance sheets.
